    "body": "### Problem\n\nNow using this function always generates `BufEnter`/`BufLeave`, and it's impossible to control.\r\n\r\nRelated issue: https://github.com/ray-x/lsp_signature.nvim/issues/260\r\n\r\n\n\n### Expected behavior\n\nOpen floating preview without `BufLeave` + `BufEnter `",
